<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Row 3: on one seat; Row 4.i: On one seat, Row 6.i: On one seat. Row 6.ii: on second seat to west of 6.i. Row 8.i: On one seat, which is broken to left.Row 8.i: On one seat, which is broken to left. Row 8.ii: On seat to west of 8.1, broken at right. Row 8.iii: a: On the 2 seats west of 8.ii. a and b: on first seat. c. On second seat; the upper left corner is lost. Row 9.i. On one seat, crudely but clearly cut. Row 9.ii. On seat to west of 9.i. Row 9.iii. On seat to west of 9.ii. Row 19.i: On seat at east end. Row 19.ii: On seat at west end, broken at both sides. Row 20.i: On seats at south end. Row 20.ii: on seat at north end. Row 21.i: on risers. Row 22.i: on seat faces. Row 22.ii: On risers. Row 26.ii: On risers</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Row 6.i: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.035</measure>. Row 6.ii: broad and shallow, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.06</measure>, cross <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.36</measure>. Row 8.i: lightly cut letters, lunate, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.04</measure>. Row 8.ii: clearly cut, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.04</measure>-<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.05</measure>. Row 8.iii: a. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.08</measure>, clearly cut, b. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.13</measure>, c. clearly cut, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.12</measure>. Row 9.i: design c.<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.30</measure>., letters <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.04</measure>-<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.07</measure>. Row 9.ii clearly cut, square letters, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.035</measure> - <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.06</measure>. Row 9.iii: monogram, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.08</measure>. Row 9.iii. On seat to west of 9.ii. Row 19.i: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.18</measure>-<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.19</measure>. Row 19.ii: letters <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.06</measure> - <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.09</measure>. Row 20.ii: Large, with broad flat trenches, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.16</measure>. Row 21.i: first pair, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03</measure> - <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.05</measure>; second pair, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.07</measure>. Row 22.i: l<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.06</measure> - <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.13</measure>. Row 22.ii: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.05</measure> and <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.07</measure>. Row 23.i: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.06</measure> - <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.15</measure>. Row 26.ii: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure> (epsilon), <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.04</measure>.</p>
</div>
